  "description": "A bright blue sky serves as the backdrop for three birds in flight. One bird, prominently featured on the left, is a seagull with white and gray plumage, wings spread wide as if caught mid-flap. Two smaller, darker birds are visible further in the distance, one slightly above and to the right of the seagull, and the other even higher and further to the right. The composition emphasizes the freedom of flight and the vastness of the sky.",
